text: Antommarchi may refer to: ==People== *François Carlo Antommarchi (1780-1838), Napoleon's physician in his exile *Hortensia Antommarchi (1850-1915), Colombian poet, sister to Dorila & Elmira *Dorila Antommarchi (1853-1923), Colombian poet, sister to Hortensia & Elmira *Elmira Antommarchi (c.1850s-?), Colombian poet, sister to Hortensia & Dorila ==Law== *Antommarchi Rights
title: Antommarchi
